*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /pɪg/

=== Noun ===
'''pig''' (''plural'' '''pigs''' or '''[[swine]]''')
#A [[mammal]] of the genus ''Sus'', often raised on [[farm]]s for [[meat]].
#A [[greedy]] person; someone who overeats or has eats rapidly and noisily.
#A [[nasty]] or [[disgusting]] person.
#*''[[capitalist]] pig'', ''[[male chauvinist]] pig''
#A [[dirty]] person.
#(''derogatory slang'') A [[police]] officer.
#A difficult problem.

====Scientific name====
*[[Sus scrofa]], [[Sus scrofa domesticus]]

